{"tid":2146344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登而家最少有兩個熱門post係fake news","createTime":"2020-08-08T13:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T14:06:26.000Z","uid":163380,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"78b977bbf71a498d12650e954f8b3856bae23d52","tid":2146344,"uid":163380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:40:43.000Z","msg":"大家睇路<br />\nshare前記得fact check<br />\n<br />\n【即時】李家超：美國不法分子已違反國安法 警方將部署執法行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2146289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2146289</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n呢個完完全全係fake news，文匯根本無呢篇<br />\n<br />\n葛珮帆 : 如果市民因為美國制裁而感到高興 有可能違反國安法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2146132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2146132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n呢個極度可疑，樓主個source 係一張直播cap 圖，仲有人post自創嘅民建聯水印infograph，已經好多人留言話fake 但無計，唔係個個人都睇cm<br />\n<br />\nfact check 呀大家，唔好一睇到對家做白痴嘢就高潮"},{"pid":"e2ed5f1297e297f4f2888800f14a83f533a06d3f","tid":2146344,"uid":73276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0585e6c1e85aaded12f1f49b17d64f40dfed04d6","tid":2146344,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82191fbf543ec5c9a33c4f2647a17d09983d2f92","tid":2146344,"uid":62570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5b97e8150a194c1320cb2ce991fcf80c0580291","tid":2146344,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:42:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac67274986705a359161c5a017be164fc6fb3ad1","tid":2146344,"uid":50581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"同一個OP嚟"},{"pid":"8ef2c05802f06383a7026255c597a6ddd3e67277","tid":2146344,"uid":321059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"兩個p